      "content": "hey so im 20 weeks pregnant and i have this really bad sinus infection that wont go away. mcmra de most stuff i find online says to avoid decongestants but i'm feeling so stuffed up i can barely breathe. is it okay if i take some Sudafed or maybe some ciprofloxacin to clear this up? i just need some relief fast.",
